# üîó Welcome to ChainPaper ## Trustless Whitepaper Platform *Secure markdown editing with cryptographic authorship verification* ---
## ‚ú® What is ChainPaper? **ChainPaper** is a revolutionary platform that combines the simplicity of markdown editing with the security of cryptographic verification. Write and prove authorship without relying on centralized servers or backends. ### üéØ Key Features - **üîí Trustless Verification** - Cryptographic proofs ensure document integrity - **‚ö° Real-time Preview** - See your formatted content as you type - **üì± Responsive Design** - Works seamlessly on desktop, tablet, and mobile - **üé® Rich Formatting** - Support for math equations, tables, emojis, and more - **üíæ No Backend Required** - Everything runs in your browser - **üì§ Export Options** - Generate PDFs, Word docs, or JSON with verification metadata --- ## üöÄ Getting Started ### 1. Try the Editor Switch between **Source** and **Reader** modes using the toggle in the footer. ### 2. Format Your Text Use the toolbar above to apply formatting: - **Bold**, *italic*, underline, ~~strikethrough~~ - Headers, lists, blockquotes, and more - Math equations: $E = mc^2$ or block equations: $$ \sum_{i=1}^{n} x_i = x_1 + x_2 + \cdots + x_n $$ ### 3. Insert Rich Content - Tables with customizable styling - Code blocks with syntax highlighting - Emojis üòä and emoticons :) - Footnotes[^1] for detailed references - Images and links ### 4. Export Your Work Generate professional documents with built-in authorship verification. --- ## üìù Sample Content ### Table Example | Feature | Status | Notes | |---------|--------|-------| | Markdown Editing | ‚úÖ | Full syntax support | | Math Rendering | ‚úÖ | KaTeX integration | | Export Options | ‚úÖ | PDF, DOCX, JSON | | Authorship Proof | ‚úÖ | Cryptographic verification | ### Code Block Example ```javascript // ChainPaper document verification function verifyDocument(document, signature) { const hash = crypto.subtle.digest('SHA-256', document); return crypto.subtle.verify('ECDSA', publicKey, signature, hash); } ``` ## üé® Alignment Examples ### This content is centered You can align any content using alignment comments. **Right-aligned text** Perfect for signatures or side notes. Justified text provides a clean, professional appearance by aligning text to both left and right margins. This is particularly useful for formal documents, academic papers, and professional reports where visual consistency is important. --- ## üí° Pro Tips > **Tip**: Use `Ctrl/Cmd + Ctrl + Space` (Mac) or `Win + .` (Windows) to access emoji picker > **Tip**: Press Enter in a list to continue the list, or Enter twice to exit > **Tip**: Use the zoom controls in the footer to adjust document size --- ## üîó Quick Links * üìñ [Documentation](https://github.com/KurutoDenzeru/ChainPaper) * üêõ [Report Issues](https://github.com/KurutoDenzeru/ChainPaper/issues) * üí¨ [Community Discussions](https://github.com/KurutoDenzeru/ChainPaper/discussions) * ‚≠ê [Star on GitHub](https://github.com/KurutoDenzeru/ChainPaper) ---
